    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简介</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015830/extras/53c2a1e7f9e94cdf3c1dc64603b7726b.poster.avif?t=1701331315\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015830/extras/53c2a1e7f9e94cdf3c1dc64603b7726b.webm?t=1701331315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015830/extras/53c2a1e7f9e94cdf3c1dc64603b7726b.mp4?t=1701331315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pingo Adventure是一款<strong>可爱</strong>的3D平台游戏，玩家将在一个充斥着<strong>物理模拟</strong>的世界尽情的与各种场景互动。<br><br><strong>探索</strong>热带雨林，古代遗迹乃至充满岩浆的地牢。同时各个场景也设计了特别为基于物理模拟的世界所打造的<strong>谜题</strong>。<br><br>不止如此，在普通的平台关卡之间也安插着各种有趣的<strong>小游戏</strong>等待收集，通关解锁之后也能于“街机模式”下不断重玩。<br><br>在漫长的冒险中也可以收集各种各样俏皮可爱的<strong>服装</strong>，打造独属于自己的Pingo!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015830/extras/f5f69ba5060ce91f0bef19a8bc66c3fe.poster.avif?t=1701331315\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015830/extras/f5f69ba5060ce91f0bef19a8bc66c3fe.webm?t=1701331315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015830/extras/f5f69ba5060ce91f0bef19a8bc66c3fe.mp4?t=1701331315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><br><strong>物理模拟</strong> - 沉浸于可互动的实时物理模拟场景<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015830/extras/05f571545b53ddbebc8d817836915831.poster.avif?t=1701331315\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com